# 🚀 Delivery Time Prediction

### 🎯 Objective

Built a machine learning model to predict food delivery time using real-world logistics data, improving operational efficiency and customer experience.

---

### ⚙️ Approach

* Cleaned and preprocessed ~39K records
* Engineered key features:

  * Traffic-adjusted distance
  * Peak-hour indicator
  * Order preparation time
* Compared models:

  * Linear Regression
  * Random Forest
  * XGBoost (final)
* Tuned using RandomizedSearchCV
* Validated with 5-fold Cross Validation

---

### 📊 Results

* **Best Model:** XGBoost
* **R²:** 0.82
* **MAE:** 3.09 minutes
* **MAPE:** 13.3%
* Stable CV MAE: ~3.11 (low variance)

---

### 🔍 Key Insights

* Delivery time driven by:

  * Rider rating
  * Traffic-adjusted distance
  * Vehicle condition & weather
* Feature engineering improved performance by ~23%

---

### 🛠️ Tech Stack

Python • Pandas • Scikit-learn • XGBoost

